ai-patthana14.33:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma ladies that are difficult for the living, etc.,
ai-patthana14.33:2.1_0: The causes of another reason doesn’t give rise to the cause or condition for the sake of extra effort.
ai-patthana14.33:2.1_1: The causes of another reason to not give rise to the cause or condition.
ai-patthana14.33:2.1_2: There are things that arise, not dependent on the teaching, and there are no cause or condition.
ai-patthana14.33:3.1_0: He doesn’t give rise to the teaching, and there is no cause or condition for the sake of defilement.
ai-patthana14.33:3.1_1: This is the section in brief.
